{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9947feb788","title":"严惩制造汉阳一中反革命暴乱罪犯　首恶分子王建国等三人已依法处决","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2ab5f088f6","index":0,"year":1957,"month":9,"day":6,"articleId":"9947feb788"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"06bbf56893","name":"新华社"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1af476e1ba","type":"title","text":"严惩制造汉阳一中反革命暴乱罪犯　首恶分子王建国等三人已依法处决","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9947feb788"},{"id":"fe3d57741a","type":"authors","text":"新华社","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9947feb788"},{"id":"4171286abf","type":"paragraph","text":"据新华社武汉６日电湖北省汉阳县人民法院今天在蔡甸镇举行的有一万多群众参加的宣判大会上宣布，制造汉阳县第一中学暴乱事件的现行反革命首恶分子王建国、钟毓文、杨焕尧三人，已经过最高人民法院批准判处死刊，并当场执行。积极参与策划暴乱事件的四名骨干分子杨松涛、胡斌、余心平和余世中，分别判处十五年到五年的有期徒刑。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9947feb788"},{"id":"305be8ce07","type":"paragraph","text":" ——原载《人民日报》1957年9月7日。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9947feb788"}],"page":{"id":"df0cc2d86e","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9947feb788","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}